//Vessels / Ureters

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 of Spine MRI

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Vessels / Ureters' from Finding dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled

And 'Vertebral artery' radio button is enabled
And 'Aorta thoracica' radio button is enabled
And 'Aorta abdominalis' radio button is enabled
And 'Common iliac artery' radio button is enabled
And 'Extern iliac artery' radio button is enabled
And 'Vena cava' radio button is enabled
And 'Ureter' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Vertebral artery' radio button
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'Occlusion' radio button is enabled
And 'Hypoplasia' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Aorta thoracica' radio button
Then 'Elongation' radio button is enabled
And 'Aneurysm' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Aneurysm' radio button
Then 'Maximum diameter' input field is enabled


When I select 'Aorta abdominalis' radio button
Then 'Elongation' radio button is enabled
And 'Aneurysm' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Aneurysm' radio button
Then 'Maximum diameter' input field is enabled


When I select 'Common iliac artery' radio button
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'Elongation' radio button is enabled
And 'Aneurysm' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Aneurysm' radio button
Then 'Maximum diameter' input field is enabled

When I select 'Extern iliac artery' radio button
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'Elongation' radio button is enabled
And 'Aneurysm' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Aneurysm' radio button
Then 'Maximum diameter' input field is enabled

When I select 'Vena cava' radio button
Then 'Occlusion' radio button is enabled
And 'Sinistral V. cava inferior' radio button is enabled
And 'Duplicated V. cava inferior' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Ureter' radio button
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
And 'Congestion' radio button is enabled
And 'Ureter duplex/fissus' radio button is enabled
